Q: Why does Terraform use state locking?
A: To prevent concurrent writes and state corruption.

Q: Why S3 gives 412 error?
A: S3 enforces conditional writes when locking is enabled.

âœ… Summary

* Error = stale Terraform state lock
* Fix = terraform force-unlock <LOCK_ID>
* Best practice = S3 + DynamoDB locking